{"text_id":19244,"tokens":["The"," Electoral"," College"," has"," been"," a"," source"," of"," controversy"," in"," the"," United"," States"," since"," its"," creation","."," On"," the"," surface",","," it"," seems"," like"," an"," antiquated"," process"," but"," the"," deeper"," purpose"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College"," serves"," as"," a"," crucial"," part"," of"," our"," democracy"," and"," should"," not"," be"," abolished","."," ","\n\n","The"," Electoral"," College"," was"," designed"," to"," grant"," fair"," and"," equal"," representation"," for"," every"," citizen"," in"," the"," United"," States","."," It"," ensures"," that"," the"," votes"," of"," more"," populated"," states"," are"," not"," completely"," dominating"," the"," election","."," By"," allowing"," even"," the"," smallest"," states"," to"," have"," an"," impact"," on"," the"," election",","," citizens"," from"," all"," different"," geographic"," regions"," can"," be"," represented"," when"," voting"," for"," the"," President","."," ","\n\n","Another"," argument"," in"," support"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College"," is"," that"," it"," maintains"," an"," even"," playing"," field"," nearly"," every"," election"," cycle","."," By"," giving"," more"," populous"," states"," an"," advantage",","," it"," creates"," a"," situation"," in"," which"," each"," state"," must"," work"," to"," build"," a"," coalition"," across"," multiple"," states"," which"," can"," challenge"," the"," more"," populated"," areas","."," This"," creates"," a"," more"," competitive"," environment"," which"," ensures"," that"," the"," eventual"," winner"," is"," the"," one"," who"," can"," bring"," together"," the"," most"," voters"," across"," the"," country","."," ","\n\n","Critics"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College"," claim"," that"," the"," process"," is"," prone"," to"," disaster","."," What"," would"," happen"," if"," the"," Electoral"," College"," did"," not"," work"," as"," intended",","," and"," one"," candidate"," distinctly"," did"," not"," have"," the"," majority"," of"," the"," popular"," vote","?"," This"," is"," a"," legitimate"," concern",","," but"," also"," highly"," unlikely","."," The"," safety"," net"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College"," would"," stop"," any"," one"," candidate"," from"," running"," away"," with"," the"," election","."," Generally",","," the"," result"," of"," an"," election"," where"," the"," Electoral"," College"," and"," the"," popular"," vote"," are"," in"," conflict"," is"," that"," the"," candidate"," who"," won"," the"," popular"," vote"," is"," more"," likely"," than"," not"," also"," the"," winner"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College","."," ","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," should"," be"," kept"," intact","."," Its"," purpose"," of"," ensuring"," fair"," and"," equal"," representation"," for"," every"," citizen"," is"," essential"," in"," a"," democracy","."," Furthermore",","," it"," provides"," a"," level"," playing"," field"," for"," all"," candidates"," on"," which"," they"," must"," compete","."," The"," disaster"," factor"," is"," real",","," but"," highly"," unlikely"," to"," occur","."," The"," Electoral"," College"," is"," necessary"," in"," the"," United"," States"," today",","," and"," should"," not"," be"," abolished","."," ","\n\n","This"," concludes"," my"," essay"," on"," the"," controversy"," surrounding"," the"," Electoral"," College"," and"," why"," it"," should"," remain"," intact","."," Thank"," you"," for"," considering"," my"," opinion","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"davinci","label":1}